  "_narrative": "**Where We Stand**\nWe're tied at 0 points with everyone else in Pool C as the tournament kicks off. Rankings suggest we match up well against #25 Ennismore and #41 Windsor, but #3 Kincardine will be a serious test.\n\n**Our Next Game**\nWe face the Ennismore Eagles on Friday April 10 at 9:15 AM in our tournament opener. On paper we have an edge over the #25-ranked Eagles, but anything can happen in tournament hockey and they'll come out hungry.\n\n**Around the Pool**\nThe other 9:15 AM game has #3 Kincardine taking on #41 Windsor - we'll want Windsor to keep that one close or pull an upset to help our pool chances. Then at 3:45 PM, we face Windsor while Ennismore battles the top-seeded Kinucks.",
